$interpreted: Emily: Congratulations!
Man: Always be in love and grow old together!

Lisa: Thank you for the blessings~
We will always be in love with each other!
Ned: So Sir Sherlock really didn't come.
Lisa: Don't mention his name. It's better that he's not here.
Ned: I say we should still visit Sir Sherlock, perhaps sometime after the wedding ceremony?
Lisa: We'll see then...
Ned: I wonder how the chat between Lisa and Sir Sherlock is going...
Ned: Emily? Why are you here?
Emily: Ned! Nice timing you got there. Quick, go after Lisa!
Ned: Lisa!? Did something happen to her?
Emily: Lisa heard that Mister Sherlock wandered into the Hazardous Zone. She is so worried about his safety that she chased after him without thinking.
Emily: I'm afraid that something bad might happen to her. Please, go after her as fast as possible!

Ned: Understood, I will go after her right now. 
I will not allow anything bad to happen to Lisa!

Sherlock: Damnit, finally fixed my body,
yet the Soul Energy driver HAD to choose this very moment to break down...
Ned: Sir Sherlock!

Ned: Sir Sherlock, are you alright?
Where is Lisa? Why isn't she with you?

Sherlock: My body was smashed to bits by the Kalta Beast.
Lisa, in an attempt to buy me time to repair myself,
Sherlock: lure the beast away herself!
Ned: What did you say!?
Sherlock: You, go rescue Lisa now. If Lisa comes out of this safe and sound, I will agree to your marriage. If you are still angry at me afterward,
Sherlock: you can punch me as much as you desire... As long as Lisa is safe, I don't give a damn about what happens to me. So please...
Ned: So you will do whatever I desire?
Sherlock: Yes, whether it's my entire property or my position as Vice President of the Commerce Chamber; you can have them all!
Ned: If so...
Ned: Then, please reconcile with Lisa!
Sherlock: That's it!?
Ned: I know the reason you target me is that you worry once Lisa and I are married, you will lose Lisa forever...

Ned: However, the truth is, 
I just got myself a new family with a wife and a father.
Sherlock: Ned, you...
Ned: You didn't lose Lisa. Therefore, even if it costs me my life, I will protect your precious daughter!
Sherlock: The Soul Energy driver is functioning again?
Ned: Does that mean Sir Sherlock can move now? Then we shall go rescue Lisa, together!
Sherlock: Got it!

Lisa: I, I just got married.
So, ummm... can you let me go?
Lisa: AHHHHHHHH!!
Ned: Lisa!
Ned: Lisa, are you alright?
Sherlock: Took me longer than expected to fix my body. Thank goodness we made it in time...
Lisa: Father, how did you and Ned...
Sherlock: He said he would gladly give his life to protect my precious daughter. If he has this kind of heart, then he is my ally~
Ned: Lisa is my wife. Naturally, it's my duty to protect her at all costs.
Sherlock: Hmph, you're a much better man than I ever expected~
Lisa: Ned, that's great news! My father has finally acknowledged you!
Sherlock: Not quite yet. Treating him as an ally and agreeing him to marry my daughter are two very different matters!
Lisa: WHAT!?
Sherlock: If you want to be acknowledged by me, find me the golden desert spheres. That's the trial for you.
Lisa: Isn't that the trial given to you by the lizard nobles!
Ned: No problem. I know where to find the golden desert spheres. I will go get them right away.
Lisa: Fa~ ther~
Sherlock: ... Ok, ok. I'll go easy on you this time and accompany you on this trip. Just this once, though!
Lisa: Then I shall accompany you guys as well!
Ned: Let's go.
